. 2021 trat Schweighöfer als Ludwig Dieter im Netflix-Film „Army of the Dead“ unter der Regie von Zack Snyder auf. Er wiederholte seine Rolle im Prequel-Film „Army of Thieves“, bei dem er auch Regie führte.","name":"Matthias Schweighöfer","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"マティアス・シュヴァイクホファー","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"ماتياس شفيغوفر","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Маттиас Швайгхёфер","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Маттіас Швайґгефер","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"מתיאס שווייגהופר","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"마티아스 슈바이크회퍼","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"馬提亞斯·史維克福","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CH","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"Matthias Schweighöfer（1981年3月11日-），德国演员、电影制片人。他最出名的是在《盗贼军团》（2021 年）和《亡灵军团》（2021 年）中饰演路德维希·迪特。","name":"马提亚斯·施维赫夫","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"馬提亞斯·史維克福（1981 年 3 月 11 日-），德